				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Canh-T%C3%BD-xu%C3%A2n/poem-07lW8--tX-z2RUCwEm7SdQ">Canh Tý xuân - 庚子春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/K%C3%BD-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-ho%C3%A0i-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-Thanh-Hi%C3%AAn-T%E1%BB%91-Nh%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-HblN2xdvYT_I8LjH-26WvQ">Ký đồng hoài đệ Thanh Hiên Tố Như tử - 寄同懷弟清軒素如子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/author-YFWZ8afu7g2IoLevX1_E2Q">Nguyễn Đề</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Minh-Khi%C3%AAm/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-ti%E1%BA%BFt-ph%E1%BB%A5/poem-K4IpZgWJ8BxcxNKQSHD-Tg">Nguyễn tiết phụ - 阮節婦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Minh-Khi%C3%AAm/author-P_O0C8eAMSSE0VWCvRAM-w">Đặng Minh Khiêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/Th%C3%A1i-tang-t%E1%BB%AD-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-Sd5Vvedx1F-6IW28phTuwQ">Thái tang tử kỳ 2 - 採桑子其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Thu%E1%BA%ADt-%C3%BD-ki%C3%AAm-tr%C3%ACnh-h%E1%BB%AFu-nh%C3%A2n-Mai-S%C6%A1n-Ph%E1%BB%A7/poem-_K4rRb6p8E9GviTEENnJSg">Thuật ý kiêm trình hữu nhân Mai Sơn Phủ - 述意兼呈友人枚山甫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-PBy92bBuBMMs53v9tc9E0A">Hồ Xuân Hương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0-H%E1%BB%99c/Th%E1%BB%A9-Tri%E1%BB%81u-Ti%C3%AAn-qu%E1%BB%91c-T%E1%BB%AB-t%E1%BB%83-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-thi-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-iSdKPTeiOhsgV-oL0L0chw">Thứ Triều Tiên quốc Từ tể tướng thi vận - 次朝鮮國徐宰相詩韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nh%C6%B0-H%E1%BB%99c/author-hBXR37XFAAQU0OmaXNOG-g">Lương Như Hộc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C3%B4ng/Ti%E1%BB%85n-n%E1%BB%99i-t%E1%BB%AD-nam-quy-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-BdoROSX7uTVzkDv79Pv75g">Tiễn nội tử nam quy kỳ 1 - 送內子南歸其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C3%B4ng/author-rfaS1tOCWjWB9PkLJ5MHxw">Nguyễn Thông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Nghi/T%E1%BB%91ng-Ph%C3%B3-D%E1%BB%AF-L%E1%BB%87-t%C3%A1-s%E1%BB%A9-An-Nam/poem-YHMf50MyXW55qtFaQdxyIQ">Tống Phó Dữ Lệ tá sứ An Nam - 送傅與礪佐使安南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Nghi/author-jF9ITDEhsPk-SGk_pW4CrQ">Tống Nghi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Duy-T%C3%B9ng/T%E1%BB%91ng-T%E1%BB%AD-V%E1%BA%A1n-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-ho%C3%A0n-L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A0nh-th%E1%BB%B1/poem-9TszU0rYgMfAnf926RyLDw">Tống Tử Vạn đệ hoàn Lê Thành thự - 送子萬弟還黎城署</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Duy-T%C3%B9ng/author-cG-6f2ETrxSYJLcjUNmVzg">Trần Duy Tùng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-T%E1%BA%AFc/Tri%E1%BB%81u-h%E1%BB%99i/poem-oBwW9u4E4WhXTJCAfLNPrw">Triều hội - 朝會</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-T%E1%BA%AFc/author-SdALrlg8daTfB8oNiho-Nw">Lê Tắc</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
